I feel your pain... I ended up having to compromise on color and weave 
on my '76 Westy's curtains.  That German-army-olive-green color is 
~impossible to find.

Anyway, PLFVW sells splitty curtain sets made from fabric that is a 
VERY close match to the original:

	http://www.plfvw.com/campers/curtains/curtains.asp

...but they're not cheap... $700 for a set.

